Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.function.attachment

Class Summary
AeAbstractAttachmentFunction Base class for attachment functions
AeCopyAllAttachmentsFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - copyAllAttachments(fromVarnames, toVarname) function call.
AeCopyAttachmentFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - copyAttachment(fromVarname, fromItemNumber, toVarname) fromVarname string containing the name of the source variable.
AeCreateAttachmentFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - createAttachment(varname, mimeType, encodedContent, [contentType]) function call.
AeGetAttachmentCountFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - getAttachmentCount(varname) function call.
AeGetAttachmentPropertyFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - getAttachmentProperty(varname,itemNumber,propertyName) function call.
AeGetAttachmentSizeFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - getAttachmentSize(varname,itemNumber) function call.
AeGetAttachmentTypeFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - getAttachmentType(varname,itemNumber) function call.
AeRemoveAllAttachmentsFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - removeAllAttachments(varnames) function call.
AeRemoveAttachmentFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - removeAttachment(varname,itemNumber) function call.
AeReplaceAttachmentFunction Class representing the function used by expression evaluators to handle the BPEL - replaceAttachment(fromVarname, fromItemNumber,toVarname, toItemNumber) function call.
